The Light Dragoons have been based at Robertson Barracks, Swanton Morley, for the past 15 years . 
 More than 4,000 people, including school children, lined the streets to say farewell to the reconnaissance unit . 
 The regiment are packing up and moving some 200 miles to their new home in Catterick, North Yorkshire . 
 Their commanding officer said it would be 'a strain to leave' after putting down 'deep roots' in Norfolk . 
 